---
// The positioning section: coastal vs. Everglades. This is the SEO thesis in UI form.
---

<section class="why">
  <div class="inner">
    <h2>Not an Everglades tour. On purpose.</h2>
    <div class="cols">
      <div class="col us">
        <h3>An Archer tour</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Launches right in Matlacha, zero drive time</li>
          <li>Saltwater flats: dolphins, manatees, stingrays</li>
          <li>Private: your group only, every trip</li>
          <li>Sandbar stops you can step out onto</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col them">
        <h3>The typical airboat ad</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>An hour-plus van ride to a swamp</li>
          <li>Gators from a crowded bench seat</li>
          <li>Scheduled departures, strangers included</li>
          <li>Same loop, every hour, all day</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cred">
      Capt. Bobby Archer has run these waters for 30 years. He built airboats before he ran
      tours on them. Nobody knows Matlacha Pass shallower.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why { padding: var(--space-section) 1.25rem; }
  .inner { max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--step-3); font-weight: 560; margin: 0 0 1.75rem; }
  .cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .col { border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem; }
  .us { background: var(--shell); box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); border-top: 4px solid var(--pine); }
  .us h3 { color: var(--pine-deep); }
  .them { background: var(--sand-deep); border-top: 4px solid transparent; }
  h3 { margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-size: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .them h3, .them li { color: var(--ink-soft); }
  ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.45rem; }
  .cred { color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: var(--measure); margin: 1.75rem 0 0; }
  @media (max-width: 44rem) { .cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
